    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09073"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1788-07-18">1788 г. июля 18.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Письмо <persName ref="people.xml#mus02">графа Пушкина</persName> о <placeName ref="places.xml#par05">Пардококском</placeName> деле, в коем имена офицеров отличившихся, принесите <date when-custom="1788-07-19">завтра</date> поутру ко мне.
                <note type="editorial">
                    A.V. Khrapovitskii writes in his diary under <date when-custom="1788-07-19">July 19 1788</date> that he was asked about the relation on the action in <placeName ref="places.xml#par05">Partakoski</placeName> and that from <persName ref="people.xml#mik02">Mikhel'son</persName>'s note it follows that all the recommended officers should be promoted to a higher rank by the <orgName ref="orgs.xml#coll04">College of War</orgName> (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#dnevni02">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskago s 18 ianvaria 1782 po 17 sentiabria 1793 goda</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 65.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
